    "Introduction to and descriptions of the concepts of ML, DL, NLP and LLMs are available (Cordella et al., 2025; Lauriola et al., 2022; Martinez-Ramon et al., 2024; Neuman et al., 2023; Sejnowski, 2024; Shahab et al., 2024; Stryker & Kavlakoglu, 2024).",
    "AI models produce a variety of outputs, including classification, clustering, prediction, decision-making (e.g., decision trees), anomaly detection, and discovery of novel patterns.",
    "Software that applies these approaches across multiple data types (e.g., text, audio, video) is referred to as multimodal GenAI (Banh & Strobel, 2023).",
    "As SLPs' tasks involve and use the same data types as inputs, this alignment gives the discipline a distinct strategic advantage.",
    "Additionally, models designed for specialized purposes do not require massive scale to be effective (Gholami & Omar, 2023)."
